description: This repository contains proof of concept for zero days and CVEs that were found by Omar Hashem through Security Research

A directory traversal vulnerability exists in the unzipDirectory functionality of WWBN AVideo 11.6 and dev master commit 3f7c0364. A specially-crafted HTTP request can lead to arbitrary command execution. An attacker can send an HTTP request to trigger this vulnerability. CVE project by @Sn0wAlice
